trans-unit.source: Provides common functionality across communication protocols for creating <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> objects from classes that are identified as Web services.
trans-unit.target: Fornece a funcionalidade comum entre os protocolos de comunicação para a criação de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> com base nas classes identificadas como serviços Web.

trans-unit.source: The abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> class and its concrete derived classes create <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> objects from classes that are identified as Web services with the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceAttribute> attribute.
trans-unit.target: O resumo <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> classe e seu concreto criar classes derivadas <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> objetos das classes que são identificados como serviços Web com o <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceAttribute> atributo.

trans-unit.source: Each concrete <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector>-derived class generates <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> objects according to a specified communication protocol; <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> provides common functionality regardless of the protocol.
trans-unit.target: Cada concreto <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector>-classe derivada gera <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> objetos de acordo com um protocolo de comunicação especificado. <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> fornece a funcionalidade comum, independentemente do protocolo.

trans-unit.source: An output <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instance can be used to generate a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document with the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.Write%2A> method or one of the available overloads.
trans-unit.target: Uma saída <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instância pode ser usada para gerar um documento WSDL Web Services Description Language () com o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.Write%2A> método ou uma das sobrecargas disponíveis.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instance can also be used by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> class and related classes to generate client proxy code or abstract server code.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instância também pode ser usada pelo <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> e classes relacionadas ao gerar o proxy do cliente de código ou abstrair o código do servidor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> class uses the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute> to create a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> for each binding it identifies in the Web service class.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> classe usa a <xref:System.Web.Services.WebServiceBindingAttribute> para criar um <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> para cada associação identifica na classe de serviço da Web.

trans-unit.source: If that attribute is not present, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> class creates a single binding for the entire class.
trans-unit.target: Se esse atributo não estiver presente, a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> classe cria uma associação simples para a classe inteira.

trans-unit.source: For each Web service method (a method in the Web service class appearing with the <xref:System.Web.Services.WebMethodAttribute>) belonging to a binding, a class derived from <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> generates an operation and associated messages that are added to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> object.
trans-unit.target: Método de serviço para cada Web (um método na classe de serviço da Web que aparecem com o <xref:System.Web.Services.WebMethodAttribute>) que pertencem a uma associação, uma classe derivada de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector> gera uma operação e mensagens associadas que são adicionadas para o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Typically, a developer uses these classes indirectly through the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionReflector> class, instead of directly invoking classes derived from <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector>.
trans-unit.target: Normalmente, um desenvolvedor usa essas classes indiretamente por meio de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionReflector> classe, em vez de invocar diretamente classes derivadas de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolReflector>.
